      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Frank Phillips</b>\n</p><p><b>Frank Phillips</b>,<br />\na British avocational computer chess programmer <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> and author of the private chess engine <a href=\"/Searcher\" title=\"Searcher\">Searcher</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1998\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1998</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Frank_Phillips&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1998\">1998</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Frank_Phillips&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1998\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=14970\">EGTB</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 10, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Edwards%27_Tablebases\" title=\"Edwards&#39; Tablebases\">Edwards' Tablebases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=18612\">Beginner's guide?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 14, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=22206\">Help a beginner</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 14, 1998</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=22226\">Re: Help a beginner</a> by <a href=\"/Don_Dailey\" title=\"Don Dailey\">Don Dailey</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 14, 1998</dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=22281\">Help a beginner(2)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 15, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=33962\">Moves per position</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 25, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=34852\">Bitboards</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 05, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=47747\">Opening book</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 01, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Opening Book</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=51233\">Hashing</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 09, 1999</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=51236\">Re: Hashing</a> by <a href=\"/Andrew_Williams\" title=\"Andrew Williams\">Andrew Williams</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 09, 1999</dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=53446\">BitBoards</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 29, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=60584\">Linux - and chess</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 15, 1999</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=62577\">WinBoard and pondering under W98</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 28, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Pondering\" title=\"Pondering\">Pondering</a>, <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a>, <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=67203\">EGTBs</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 03, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Nalimov_Tablebases\" title=\"Nalimov Tablebases\">Nalimov Tablebases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=73649\">Forward pruning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 16, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Pruning\" title=\"Pruning\">Pruning</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=73701\">Re: Forward pruning</a> by <a href=\"/Andrew_Williams\" title=\"Andrew Williams\">Andrew Williams</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 16, 1999</dd></dl>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Frank_Phillips&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=125295\">singular extension</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 20, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Singular_Extensions\" title=\"Singular Extensions\">Singular Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=144413\">Root move and incomplete iteration</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 11, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Root\" title=\"Root\">Root</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=144432\">Re: Root move and incomplete iteration</a> by <a href=\"/Robert_Hyatt\" title=\"Robert Hyatt\">Robert Hyatt</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 11, 2000</dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=169297\">Linux</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 12, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=171919\">CCT3 Day 1 reflections</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 27, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/CCT3\" title=\"CCT3\">CCT3</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=172027\">CCT3 day2</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 28, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=216120\">3 fold repetiton (Seacher v Postmodernist)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 02, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Repetitions\" title=\"Repetitions\">Repetitions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=247236\">king and pawns ending</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 23, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Pawn_Endgame\" title=\"Pawn Endgame\">Pawn Endgame</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=315666\">Easy mate</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 13, 2003 <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Frank_Phillips&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=489978\">History pruning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 27, 2006&#160;» <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=21543\">magic move - bitboard orientation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 01, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=26542\">core2 popcnt</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 13, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Population_Count\" title=\"Population Count\">Population Count</a>, <a href=\"/X86-64\" title=\"X86-64\">x86-64</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=27229\">malloc more than 2GB&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 28, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=27722\">Bitbases</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Frank Phillips</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 03, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Endgame_Bitbases\" title=\"Endga